description: Embracing the art of hospitality, Echelon is a one-of-a-kind urban resort style living opportunity for residents and investors. Discover this rare 11th floor 1 BR 1 BA with partial Harbor view and a square layout that maximizes space efficiency, and it also comes with a deeded garage parking space! Featuring an elongated living room that can fit a full set of sofa and a dining table, a bedroom room with two closets, and a spa like marble bath en-suite with linen closets. Finishes include wide white oak wood plank flooring throughout, custom Italian cabinetry, Thermador integrated appliances, and oversized window walls equipped with motorized shade. Echelon residents enjoy 24/7 Concierge service and over 50,000 sq.ft of amenities including 1 indoor and 2 outdoor pools as well as state of the art fitness facilities including an indoor basketball court, golf simulator and yoga studio.
